1 Right click on the download and choose "Bandwith alocation" to HIGH

2 Right click on the download and select the UP and DOWN speeds to UNLIMITED, please not that it IS important to keep the upload speed unlimited, otherwise the transfere will be (somehow) slow

3 On the preferences of the program (any torrent program should have this) go to transfers /connections/bandwith allocation and set the number of conections like in 5000, the other number below that, also set it to 500 or 500, this is just to make it able to connect to more seeders at a time, also this increases the chances of catching a seeder like me that will be uploading at speeds probably faster than your average download speeds.
